  "shap_base_value": 0.50014,
  "shap_note": "For each sample row in sample_predictions.csv, the model output is approximately shap_base_value + sum(all feature SHAP values). The driver_k_feature / driver_k_shap columns list the top-10 features by |SHAP| for that row; sign indicates direction (+ pushes fire risk up, - pushes it down). SHAP values are on the model's raw margin scale for tree models, not probability.",
  "imputation": "median (SimpleImputer)",
  "preprocessing_steps": [
    "1. avg_wind_speed: clip(lower=0)",
    "2. min_temp: set to NaN if < -20 F (API error)",
    "3. precipitation = log1p(precipitation) \u2014 applied IN-PLACE",
    "4. log_elevation = log1p(elevation)",
    "5. log_wind_speed = log1p(avg_wind_speed)",
    "6. temp_range = (max_temp - min_temp).clip(lower=0)",
    "7. Lag features: precip_lag_7/14 = groupby(hex_id).shift(7/14)",
    "8. Rolling: precip_rolling_7/30, max_temp_rolling_7, wind_rolling_7",
    "9. drought_index = 30-day rolling sum of (precip_median - precip).clip(0)",
    "10. VPD via Tetens formula from max/min temp",
    "11. Rate-of-change + acceleration features (7-day deltas)",
    "12. Cyclical encoding: month_sin/cos, doy_sin/cos",
    "13. Drop rows with NaN in precip_lag_14, precip_rolling_30, drought_index",
    "14. Impute remaining NaN with median"
  ]
}